00:00:19,259 --> 00:00:22,478
(narrator) Russia: mid-June 1941.

3
00:00:22,559 --> 00:00:25,505
A bewildered, uncertain country.

4
00:00:25,589 --> 00:00:29,921
Rumours abounded
of invasion by Hitler's Germany.

5
00:00:47,803 --> 00:00:51,752
Here in the Kremlin, Russia's leaders
seemed oblivious of the Nazi threat,

6
00:00:51,831 --> 00:00:53,784
or if not oblivious, then complacent,

7
00:00:53,903 --> 00:00:57,809
as if, by ignoring it,
it might disappear.

8
00:01:03,379 --> 00:01:07,361
Yet already, millions of German troops
were poised along Russia's border

9
00:01:07,445 --> 00:01:10,238
to launch the bloodiest land battle
in history -

10
00:01:10,323 --> 00:01:14,197
the battle that was eventually
to decide the Second World War.

11
00:02:09,366 --> 00:02:13,502
(crowd)
Ein Volk, ein Reich, ein Führer!

12
