Ei bloß wegen dem Schingderassa,
Bumderassasa...

19
00:02:33,574 --> 00:02:37,906
(narrator) Hitler in July 1940,
returning from France in triumph,

20
00:02:37,986 --> 00:02:40,594
stood at the pinnacle of his power.

21
